attributes.description:
Experience the legacy of Toyota Gazoo racing when you get behind the wheel of the all-new Corolla Cross GR-Sport. Its specially tuned GR-S suspension delivers sharper steering, better handling and braking for more stability during extreme cornering so you can cross boundaries on every adventure.

This 2022 Toyota Corolla Cross with only 159 km is packed with extras such as:
- LED headlights 
- Black leather sports seats 
- Contrasting red stitching throughout the interior 
- 18 inch rims 
- Cruise control 
- Voice control 
- Dual zone climate control 
- Bluetooth connectivity 
- Automatic folding mirrors
- Black roof rails 
- Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
- Lane keep assist
- Blind spot assist 
- PDC front & rear
- Automotive high beam assist and much more
